contains the password 

00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:45.866
for our Windows client.

00:00:50.632 --> 00:00:55.000
To invoke crowbar, we specify 
the protocol,

00:00:56.307 --> 00:00:58.066
the target server,

00:00:59.079 --> 00:01:00.766
a username,

00:01:01.973 --> 00:01:03.300
a wordlist,

00:01:04.705 --> 00:01:07.033
